---
# GlanceHUD static analysis policy.
Checks: >
  clang-analyzer-*,
  bugprone-*,
  performance-*,
  modernize-*,
  cppcoreguidelines-*,
  readability-*,
  -modernize-use-trailing-return-type,
  -readability-identifier-length,
  -cppcoreguidelines-avoid-magic-numbers,
  -readability-magic-numbers
WarningsAsErrors: ''
HeaderFilterRegex: 'core/(include|src)/.*'
FormatStyle: file
